Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ada orang di situ!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sedang tidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aroma ini! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, bangunlah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya. Dia mengintai target sampai pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa dia tidur di situ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tempat dudukku.\NAku tidak menyangka ini terjadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tadi aku tak sengaja\Nduduk di pangkuan Akiraâ€¦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menindihnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berciuman lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa cuma aku yang menginginkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa orang-orang biasanya\Nmenginginkan hal itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau aku ingin menciumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa tidak kulakukan saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada orang lain di sini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa aku harus minta izin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.93,0:01:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi kami kan berpacaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ha-Hanya kecupan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sekitar sini... Di sekitar sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rahasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rahasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tapi sepertinya\Ntidak ada orang lain yang melihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Apa ada orang lain di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau sudah bangun dari tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rahasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah selesai menyalinnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak ada rencana keluar lagi hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Aku cuma perlu\Nmenyelesaikan laporan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah jam segini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau boleh pulang sekarang.\NTerima kasih untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Terima kasih untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fiuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah seminggu sejak dia bilang\Nkami berencana untuk tinggal bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami bahkan belum pernah\Npulang bersama sekali pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan kami akan membahas\Nsoal tinggal bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah keburu semangat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencari properti daring tiap hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada masalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, em...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir mungkin\Nkita bisa pulang bersama hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin masih agak lama,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau mau menungguku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja! Aku akan tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti pasti sudah larut malam, jadi mungkin\Nkau bisa menginap di tempatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menginap?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fiuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, maaf aku lama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Kita akan ke tempatmu, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kita batalkan saja acara menginapnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, jangan dibatalkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, kita bisa mampir ke minimarket\Nuntuk membeli sesuatu dan makan malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa membeli set losion wajah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada merek yang kau suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em... Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, pembersih riasan dan sikat gigi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belanjanya cepat sekali! Jauh lebih mudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak perlu memanggil petugas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa ukuran celana dalammu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pfft!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka punya M dan L.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, M.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar aku yang bayar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan obrolan soal pakaian dalam\Nsama sekali tidak membuatnya gugup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah dewasa... Dewasa sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu karena dia sudah terbiasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku sudah sampai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang pernah\Nke sini sebelumnya, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menginap...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menginap hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di rumah pria! Di rumah pacarku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau cemas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tampak sangat gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir karena kita berencana\Nuntuk tinggal bersama,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita harus mencoba menginap sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terlalu terburu-buru.\NMaafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar! Tinggal bersama itu\Nseperti menginap setiap hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melewati semua langkahnya\Ndan langsung mencari properti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa bersama Akira setiap hari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Argh! Aku malu sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar berlebihan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kelihatan cemas sekali?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, apa sebaiknya\Nkita menginap di lain hari saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin mencoba menginap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Ayo menginap di sini malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti lapar. Silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya! Aku lapar sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, aku ingin mengajakmu berkeliling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau sudah menunjukkan semuanya\Nsaat pertama kali aku datang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada tempat yang belum kutunjukkan padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pintunya ada di sebelah kanan pintu masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kamar tidurku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamar tempat kau biasa tidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau berjalan di sisi kanan ranjang,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada lampu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tidur di ruang depan.\NKau bisa tidur di sini malam ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidur di ranjang Akira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terakhir, biar kutunjukkan kamar mandinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan mandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}telanjang di rumah Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tapi... apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa malu, tapi agak bersemangat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedikit senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertama kalinya aku menginap,\Ndan aku malah begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku akan baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau di sana?\NAku mendengar suara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Aku sedang duduk di sofa.\NSisi sebelahnya kosong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia mengeringkan rambutnya, 'kan?\NAku akan mengambil pengering rambut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Manusia tak kasatmata\Ntidak mengeringkan rambutnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambut dan kulit kami sangat berbeda\Ndengan manusia. Jadi tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan, itu tidak baik untuk rambutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuambilkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia punya alat itu\Nkalau tidak memakainya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena terkadang ada yang menginap?\NSeperti Karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah terbiasa melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin mantan pacarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira itu orang dewasa dan sangat baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar saja kalau dia punya pacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, ini momen yang membahagiakan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya begitu, tapi pikiranku\Nmalah ke mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia juga mengeringkan\Nrambut mantan pacarnya seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mengajaknya berpacaran\Ndengan niat menikah juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak, tidak! Jangan dibayangkan!\NNanti aku sedih sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa terasa geli?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:12:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku ingin menciummu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... Jangan dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingin melakukan hal\Nyang membuatku terburu-buru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terburu-buru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, selamat tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terburu-buru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya akan jadi terburu-buru\Nkalau kami berciuman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengan Karma?\NAku tidak melihatnya lagi akhir-akhir ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, dia kembali ke tokonya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat penyelidikan yang diikuti Karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menggunakan sedikit kutukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang dia akan berjuang di toko\Nseperti yang dilakukan Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, kau keren sekali!\NAku juga harus berjuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, tentu saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa dengannya? Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em, ada yang ingin kutanyakan juga padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dan Madaraito, apa yang membuat\Nkalian memutuskan tinggal bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan soal pekerjaan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Efisiensi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lama sekali kau baru bisa\Nmenjawab sesingkat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan membahasnya denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti penyakit pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaan detektif itu mengorek\Ninformasi dari banyak orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membicarakan hal pribadi membuatku defensif.\NAku tidak suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu, kau malu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, diamlah.\NJangan bertanya blak-blakan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm... Padahal aku berharap\Ndapat nasihat yang bermanfaat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}boleh aku bertanya\Npada Madaraito soal ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berani-berani membukakan\Nmulut besarmu itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kami mulai tinggal bersama\Nsaat Daichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, apa kalian akan tinggal bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengetahui cara kami mulai tinggal bersama\Ntidak akan membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kan tidak meminta nasihat langsung\Npadaku soal tinggal bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ada hal lain\Nyang ingin kau mintai saran?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu, ada...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome itu pria yang sangat baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai menyombongkan dia, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia itu terlalu baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut akan bergantung padanya\Ndalam segala hal kalau begini terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu, Tonome terlalu perhatian padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar! Begitulah rasanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tidak bilang padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal dia begitu baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan padanya atau terima saja.\NKalian perlu menemukan keseimbangannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal apakah itu akan membuahkan hasil ideal,\Nitu urusan lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk akal juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, aku membawakan\Nubi panggang untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, sudah lama aku tidak makan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kubagi menjadi dua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa "Ah" tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku mencicipi ubimu juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Ya, tentu saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku salah membaginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! I-Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memanfaatkan kebutaanku, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, kau itu supadari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kupotong ubinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Supa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kikira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa artinya "supadari"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh... Akira, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya, aku menuntut\Nbegitu banyak hal darimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kau menilaiku terlalu tinggi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertanya pada Kikira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Supadari"? Cari sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, aku ingin tahu\Narti umumnya, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang ingin kubicarakan denganmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ugh. Kalian berdua ini merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Supadari" itu singkatan\Ndari "super darling".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Super...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di komunitas tertentu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}artinya pria sempurna\Nyang memancarkan aura tak tergoyahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sempurna? Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cerdas, tinggi, dan berpenghasilan tinggi,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kepribadiannya baik, dari keluarga\Nbaik-baik, tampan, dan pintar urus rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Supadari adalah orang\Nyang punya semua sifat ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}biasanya ahli waris...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ahli waris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau raja minyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku itu raja minyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, kau tidak bisa melihatku,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makanya kau menafsirkan semuanya\Nterlalu positif!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, rendah hati sekali! Baik hati pula!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, maksudmu\Naku terlalu perhatian padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, aku saja yang egois karena\Nmengeluh saat diperlakukan dengan baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan saja aku pernah membahasnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, terima kasih\Nsudah mengangkat topik yang sulit ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak, bukan apa-apa kok...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah... Dia begitu menjaga perasaanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu bukan karena aku supadari\Natau semacamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma ingin mendapatkan kepercayaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em... maksudmu,\Nkau merasa aku tidak memercayaimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, tentu saja\Naku tidak bermaksud begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Apa alasannya\Nsulit untuk diungkapkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kurasa tidak adil memberi alasan\Nsaat kau merasa cemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat! Itu maksudku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ah, benar. Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu, orang tak kasatmata sebagai suatu ras
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}biasanya bekerja sebagai mata-mata\Ndan sejenisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah kenapa cuma ada sedikit catatan\Nsoal masa lalu kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan asal-usul kami\Ntidak diketahui secara pasti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun kami dihargai\Nkarena tidak terlihat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebagai ras, orang tak kasatmata kesulitan\Nmeraih kepercayaan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat masih muda,\Naku diajari tentang cara berperilaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibilang cara membaur di masyarakat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perbedaan kalian dari ras lain\Nhanya tubuh kalian tidak terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa hal itu membuat kalian\Nsulit dipercaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak terlihat, hanya itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagimu, orang tak kasatmata\Ntidak ada bedanya dengan ras lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Maaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, itu pemikiran yang membahagiakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa menjadi tak terlihat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuat orang tak kasatmata\Nmerasa kesulitan dalam hidup?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beberapa tahun lalu, muncul\Nseorang model fesyen tak kasatmata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Visual yang ditampilkannya memanfaatkan\Nciri khas orang tak kasatmata
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan cukup membuat heboh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tak kasatmata mulai dikenal\Nsebagai ras, dan kami pun mulai dipahami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah... Jarang sekali ada\Norang tak kasatmata yang jadi model?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin dia orang tak kasatmata pertama\Nyang jadi model.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah pensiun sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku bertemu dengannya saat kecil,\Ndan dia menyelamatkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Kau mengenalnya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga alasanku\Nmengekspresikan diri lewat pakaian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam pikiranku, dia sudah seperti kakak,\Natau teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata ada sosok seperti itu di hidupmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini, aku akan berusaha\Nsupaya tidak terlalu perhatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai permulaan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kumakan donat ini di depanmu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm, jadi kau memulainya dari situ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menginap malam ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya aku gugup sekali,\Ntapi Akira tetap seperti biasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku sudah baik-baik saja sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyatanya, aku malah malu sekali
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena sempat mengira kami akan bermesraan\Nlebih intim dari biasanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, apa maksudnya\Nbermesraan lebih intim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Argh! Astaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini yang namanya antiklimaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai suatu ras, orang tak kasatmata\Nkesulitan mendapat kepercayaan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum bisa memberitahunya\Nalasan sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus membicarakan ini dengannya\Nsuatu saat nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingin memberitahunya...
